# Hovercraft Challenge

## Objective
Students designed and built mini hovercraft prototypes using lightweight materials and simple motors.
A collection of practical STEM activities designed for classrooms, workshops, and outreach programmes.

These projects aim to make engineering concepts accessible through hands-on learning.
  
## Concepts covered
- Newton’s Third Law
- friction reduction
- weight balance
- iterative design

